    <p><strong>Hormuz duration:</strong> LOW. Diplomatic signals are contradictory. Duration could range from weeks to months.</p>
    <p><strong>Inflation return risk:</strong> MEDIUM. 40-50% probability of April CPI exceeding 5% if diesel stays above GHS 14.</p>
  </div>

